name: Climbing Fartlek #1
description:
A classic 'over/under' session, working above and below your FTP. Developing from the very first weeks of the Climbing Focussed Plan, where we were alternating cadences, then into steady threshold efforts. This is a great session to bring on your climbing abilities. 



In this session, you will need to call on these elements to complete the workout effectively.
